<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1920240-is-this-a-stand-alone-or-do-you-need-to">Is this a stand-alone or do you need to read the entire Otori series? If you read the sequels, would you say it&#39;s worth it?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1920240'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F77160.Across_the_Nightingale_Floor">like</a></span>

